==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Encysted
<hw>En*cyst"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Inclosed in a cyst,
or a sac, bladder, or vesicle; <as>as, an <ex>encysted</ex>
tumor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The encysted venom, or poison bag, beneath the adder's fang.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Encystment</ent>⟦br⟧
